<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Redeem Your Coins - Paper Plane Adventure</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            background: #ff8800;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .header img {
            max-width: 100px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .content h1 {
            color: #000;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #ff5e00;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            background: #f1f1f1;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #ff5e00;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/e-Xc120M7j4ctEnAJYtW06I4i1vt92LP0lxXvz6LRqAQsJu6UpwA7wlfN78NPwjb-68=w240-h480-rw" alt="Paper Plane Adventure Logo">
            <h1>Paper Plane Adventure</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi <strong><%= fullName %></strong>,</p>
            <p>Welcome to <strong>Paper Plane Adventure</strong>! We hope you're enjoying your journey with us.</p>

            <p>Here is your current coin status:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Redeemed Coins:</strong> <%= redeemed_Coins %></li>
                <li><strong>Remaining Coins:</strong> <%= remainingCoins %></li>
            </ul>

            <p>If you have any questions or encounter any issues, feel free to reach out to us at <a href="mailto:inquiry.paperplane@gmail.com">inquiry.paperplane@gmail.com</a>.</p>

            <!-- <a href="<%= redeemUrl %>" class="button">Redeem Your Coins</a> -->

            <p>Thank you for being a valued part of the Paper Plane Adventure community!</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>The Paper Plane Adventure Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Paper Plane Adventure. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="https://www.paperplaneadventure.com/privacy-policy.html" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a> | 
                <a href="https://www.paperplaneadventure.com/terms.html" target="_blank">Terms and Conditions</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
